data.description: DON'T MISS THIS LAKE WORTH GEM! This 3 bed/1 bath Old Spanish style house will WOW you with all it has to  offer! There's NO HOA, so bring your trucks and boats! Are you ready for this?? There's also  a BASEMENT & outdoor storage room! Talk about convenient? This house is SECONDS away from Interstate 95! It's  a very short distance from downtown Lake Worth and via 95 you are only about 8 minutes from Palm Beach  International Airport, Rosemary Square restaurants/shops, AND the infamous, Palm Beach Island's, Worth Avenue!
